    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1896-01-13T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1896-01-13T00:00:00-05:00" n="452"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d452">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Olney</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Bayard</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1896-01-13">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 13, 1896</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Cabled you yesterday respecting case of Hammond, American citizen, arrested and
                    in danger at Johannesburg or Pretoria. Other American citizens, it seems, are
                    also arrested and in peril. Please ask good offices of British representatives
                    in South Africa for all of them.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Olney.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
